title: Pine Ridge Apartments 2BR Includes a Garage! Beautiful St. Croix Falls
posting_body: ['Please go to youtube and search "Pine Ridge Apartments 2 Bedroom" for a video tour.', 'We will have a fantastic 2nd floor corner 2BR unit available for a September 1st move in at Pine Ridge Apartments in beautiful St. Croix Falls, WI.', '$750/month includes Garage!', 'Tenant pays heat, electric, water.', 'Very nice 800 sq ft apartment with dishwasher and a small patio off the living room.', 'Smoke free building.', 'No Pets.', '$800 Security Deposit.', 'Coin-op laundry in building.', 'Please call 651-Three-one-seven-98-one-one rather than text or email.', 'Leave message we will return your call during normal business hours.', '1 year lease required.', 'Income 3X rent.', 'Good credit/landlord references.', 'No prior eviction or felony.', 'No S8.', 'No DWI/DUI.', 'Unit shown in photos may not be exactly the same as the unit available.']
